OL,3,CSouth West Water to spend billions on
OL,4,C'environmental commitments'
OL,6,FSouth West Water has committed to
OL,7,Fspending a record #2.5 billion on
OL,8,Fimprovements to the environment over a
OL,9,Ffive-year period.
OL,11,FThe water company has pledged to
OL,12,Fnearly double its environmental
OL,13,Finvestments between 2025 and 2030 in
OL,14,Forder to improve water quality,
OL,15,Fbiodiversity and water supplies.
OL,17,FIt is part of the "largest commitment
OL,18,Fever" made by water companies to the
OL,19,FEnvironment Agency's Water Industry
OL,20,FNational Environment Programme (WINEP).
