OL,3,CSouth West Water to spend billions on
OL,4,C'environmental commitments'
OL,6,FAs part of the funding, South West
OL,7,FWater has committed to building two
OL,8,Fnew reservoirs in Somerset and
OL,9,Freducing the amount of water taken
OL,10,Ffrom the River Camel in Cornwall.
OL,12,FMark Worsfold, South West Water's
OL,13,FDirector of Asset Management, said:
OL,14,F"The WINEP programme for 2025 to 2030
OL,15,Frepresents the largest environment
OL,16,Fprogramme we have ever invested in
OL,17,Fwith over #1bn being spent to deliver
OL,18,Faround 2,200 improvements across the
OL,19,Fregion.
