OL,3,CSouth West Water to spend billions on
OL,4,C'environmental commitments'
OL,6,F"These commitments help protect the
OL,7,Fquantity and quality of our most
OL,8,Fprecious resource, which is essential
OL,9,Fto meet the future needs of both
OL,10,Fpeople and the environment."
OL,12,FThe investment announcement comes as
OL,13,FSouth West Water have said they will
OL,14,Fraise dividends to shareholders as
OL,15,Fthey confirmed consumer bill increases
OL,16,Fof 32% and 23%, respectively, over the
OL,17,Fcoming five years.
