OL,6,FSouth West Water's parent company
OL,7,FPennon said it had agreed the bill
OL,8,Fincreases negotiated with regulator
OL,9,FOfwat last year.
OL,11,FThe regulator's decision, made in
OL,12,FDecember, means the typical billpayer
OL,13,Facross the UK will see their payments
OL,14,Frise by an average of #86 this April.
OL,16,FThe group's chief executive Susan Davy
OL,17,Fsaid the company has "listened to
OL,18,Fcustomers" and that the bill rises
OL,19,Fwould pay for "record levels of
OL,20,Finvestment".
